data.description: Welcome to Valley view Horse and Hobby farm! This is a beautiful unique property with gorgeous views and for all the animal lovers who wish to pamper their animals with a 46x48 tongue and groove barn w-a large hay loft, 9-8x8 stalls or 5 full stalls with a heated track room. Barn is equipped with its own well and electric. This property has 12.85 acres to start.10 minutes from the Brookfield State Forest w-130 miles of maintained horse trails. Storage? we got it covered with a 40x26 four stall garage and a 40x16 carport. Home and barn currently sit on 3.26 acres bountiful with perennials and apple trees, pears, red and black raspberry bushes and blueberries. 9.58 acres is across the road to add to your hobby farm. Inside features a large expansive kitchen with newer appliances. 2 full updated bathrooms and 3 bedrooms. Upstairs you'll enjoy the large living room with plenty of windows for a picturesque view of the Unadilla River Valley. This is equipped with high-speed fiber internet service, for anyone that works from home. Please come see this amazing property with all it has to offer, you'll be sorry you didn't!
